### 1. Login Admin
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeCode": "ADMIN001",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. Login BT (Bí thư)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeCode": "00040280",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. Login PBT (Phó Bí thư)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeCode": "00040300",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 4. Login CU (Chi ủy)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeCode": "00050593",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 5. Test Admin route (thay TOKEN_ADMIN)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/test/admin-only
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_ADMIN

### 6. Test BT route (thay TOKEN_BT)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/test/bt-only
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_BT

### 7. Test Dashboard (BT/PBT đều vào được)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/test/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_BT_OR_PBT

### 8. Test CU cố vào route Admin (should fail 403)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/test/admin-only
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_CU

### 9. Get user info
GET http://localhost:4000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
